_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construcción con expertos del dominio y alineación iterativa con ontologías de referencia"@es .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construction avec des experts métier et alignement itératif avec des ontologies de référence"@fr .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construction with domain experts and iterative alignment with reference ontologies"@en .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construcție cu experți din domeniu și aliniere iterativă cu ontologii de referință"@ro .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-construção com especialistas no domínio e alinhamento iterativo com ontologias de referência"@pt .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Co-costruzione con esperti di dominio e allineamento iterativo con ontologie di riferimento"@it .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Samskaping med fagpersoner og iterativ tilpasning til referanseontologier"@no .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology> "Συνεκπόνηση με ειδικούς του τομέα και επαναληπτική ευθυγράμμιση με πρότυπες οντολογίες"@el .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringTool> "Protégé 5.6.9" .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#usedOntologyEngineeringTool> "VSCodium 1.92.2" .
_:genid1 <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#version> "1.0.0" .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "A ontologia OSO estrutura os observatórios marinhos em três níveis hierárquicos: infraestruturas regionais, locais e plataformas. Suporta a gestão FAIR de dados, a interoperabilidade e a integração de informações sobre infraestruturas marinhas, especialmente no contexto do EMSO ERIC."@pt .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "L'ontologia OSO struttura gli osservatori marini in tre livelli gerarchici: infrastrutture regionali, siti e piattaforme. Supporta la gestione FAIR dei dati, l'interoperabilità e l'integrazione delle informazioni sulle infrastrutture marine, in particolare nel contesto EMSO ERIC."@it .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "L'ontologie OSO structure les observatoires marins en trois niveaux hiérarchiques : infrastructures régionales, sites et plateformes. Elle soutient la gestion FAIR des données, l'interopérabilité et l'intégration des informations sur les infrastructures marines, notamment dans le cadre d'EMSO ERIC."@fr .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "La ontología OSO estructura los observatorios marinos en tres niveles jerárquicos: infraestructuras regionales, sitios y plataformas. Apoya la gestión FAIR de datos, la interoperabilidad y la integración de información sobre infraestructuras marinas, especialmente en el contexto de EMSO ERIC."@es .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "OSO-ontologien strukturerer marine observatorier i tre hierarkiske nivåer: regionale fasiliteter, steder og plattformer. Den støtter FAIR datastyring, interoperabilitet og integrasjon av informasjon om marine infrastrukturer, spesielt i EMSO ERIC-konteksten."@no .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "Ontologia OSO structurează observatoarele marine în trei niveluri ierarhice: facilități regionale, situri și platforme. Susține gestionarea FAIR a datelor, interoperabilitatea și integrarea informațiilor despre infrastructuri marine, în special în contextul EMSO ERIC."@ro .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "The OSO ontology structures marine observatories into three hierarchical levels: Regional Facilities, Sites, and Platforms. It supports FAIR data management, interoperability, and integration of heterogeneous marine infrastructure information, particularly within the EMSO ERIC framework."@en .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "Η οντολογία OSO οργανώνει τα θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια σε τρία ιεραρχικά επίπεδα: περιφερειακές υποδομές, τοποθεσίες και πλατφόρμες. Υποστηρίζει τη διαχείριση δεδομένων σύμφωνα με τις αρχές FAIR, τη διαλειτουργικότητα και την ενσωμάτωση πληροφοριών για θαλάσσιες υποδομές, ιδιαίτερα στο πλαίσιο του EMSO ERIC."@el .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/bibliographicCitation> "OSO – Observatories of the Seas Ontology (OSO). Version 1.0.0. EMSO ERIC / Ifremer. FAIRsharing DOI: 10.25504/FAIRsharing.654931."@en .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://semver.org/> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://www.conventionalcommits.org/> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://www.w3.org/TR/owl2-overview/> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://www.w3.org/TR/prov-o/> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://www.w3.org/TR/skos-reference/> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat-3/> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#EMSO_DMSG> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/coverage> "Acoperire globală (cu accent pe mările europene); acoperire temporală de la ~1990 până în prezent."@ro .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/coverage> "Cobertura global (com foco nos mares europeus); cobertura temporal desde ~1990 até o presente."@pt .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/coverage> "Cobertura global (enfocada en los mares europeos); cobertura temporal desde ~1990 hasta la actualidad."@es .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/coverage> "Copertura globale (con focus sui mari europei); copertura temporale dal ~1990 ad oggi."@it .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/coverage> "Couverture mondiale (accent sur les mers européennes) ; couverture temporelle depuis environ 1990 jusqu'à aujourd'hui."@fr .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/coverage> "Global (focus on European Seas); temporal coverage from ~1990 to present."@en .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/coverage> "Global dekning (fokus på europeiske havområder); tidsmessig dekning fra ca. 1990 til i dag."@no .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/coverage> "Παγκόσμια κάλυψη (εστίαση στις ευρωπαϊκές θάλασσες)· χρονική κάλυψη από περίπου το 1990 έως σήμερα."@el .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2025-04-04"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <https://orcid.org/0009-0008-1759-5254> .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Ontologi som beskriver kyst- og dyphavsobservatorier, inkludert alle EMSO-observatorier, som del av den europeiske tverrfaglige infrastrukturen for havbunn og vannsøyle. Må ikke forveksles med OpenScienceOntology (OSO)."@no .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Ontologia che descrive gli osservatori marini costieri e d'altura, compresi tutti gli osservatori EMSO, nell'ambito dell'infrastruttura europea multidisciplinare dei fondali marini e della colonna d'acqua. Da non confondere con OpenScienceOntology (OSO)."@it .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Ontologia que descreve os observatórios costeiros e de mar aberto, incluindo todos os observatórios EMSO no âmbito da infraestrutura europeia multidisciplinar dos fundos marinhos e da coluna de água. Não deve ser confundida com OpenScienceOntology (OSO)."@pt .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Ontologie care descrie observatoarele marine de coastă și de larg, inclusiv toate observatoarele EMSO, ca parte a infrastructurii europene multidisciplinare a fundului mării și a coloanei de apă. A nu se confunda cu OpenScienceOntology (OSO)."@ro .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Ontologie décrivant les observatoires marins côtiers et hauturiers, incluant l’ensemble des observatoires EMSO, dans le cadre de l'infrastructure européenne multidisciplinaire dédiée aux fonds marins et à la colonne d’eau. À ne pas confondre avec l'OpenScienceOntology (OSO)."@fr .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Ontology describing coastal and open seas observatories, including all EMSO observatories as part of the European Multidisciplinary Seafloor and Water Column Observatories infrastructure. Not to be confused with the OpenScienceOntology (OSO)."@en .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Ontología que describe los observatorios marinos costeros y de alta mar, incluyendo todos los observatorios EMSO en el marco de la infraestructura europea multidisciplinar para el fondo marino y la columna de agua. No debe confundirse con OpenScienceOntology (OSO)."@es .
_:genid1 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Οντολογία που περιγράφει τα παράκτια και ανοιχτά θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια, συμπεριλαμβανομένων όλων των παρατηρητηρίων EMSO, στο πλαίσιο της ευρωπαϊκής πολυκλαδικής υποδομής για τον πυθμένα και τη στήλη του νερού. Να μην συγχέεται με το OpenScienceOntology (OSO)."@el .
