_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontologi som beskriver forholdet mellom regionale fasiliteter, steder, plattformer, forskningsinfrastrukturer, organisasjoner, cruiser og de ansvarlige på hvert nivå."@no .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontologia che descrive le relazioni tra strutture regionali, siti, piattaforme, infrastrutture di ricerca, organizzazioni, crociere e i responsabili di ciascun livello."@it .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontologia que descreve as relações entre instalações regionais, locais, plataformas, infraestruturas de investigação, organizações, cruzeiros e os responsáveis por cada nível."@pt .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontologie care descrie relațiile dintre facilitățile regionale, siturile, platformele, infrastructurile de cercetare, organizațiile, croazierele și persoanele responsabile la fiecare nivel."@ro .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontologie décrivant les relations entre les nœuds régionaux, les sites, les plateformes, les infrastructures de recherche, les organisations, les campagnes à la mer et les personnes responsables à chaque niveau."@fr .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontology describing the relationships between Regional Facilities, Sites, Platforms, Research Infrastructures, Organisations, Cruises, and the persons in charge of each level."@en .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontología que describe las relaciones entre instalaciones regionales, emplazamientos, plataformas, infraestructuras de investigación, organizaciones, cruceros y las personas responsables de cada nivel."@es .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Οντολογία που περιγράφει τις σχέσεις μεταξύ περιφερειακών υποδομών, τοποθεσιών, πλατφορμών, ερευνητικών υποδομών, οργανισμών, αποστολών και των υπευθύνων σε κάθε επίπεδο."@el .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Observatories of the Seas Ontology (OSO)"@en .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ontologi for marine observatorier (OSO)"@no .
