_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ontologia dos observatórios marinhos (OSO)"@pt .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ontologia observatoarelor marine (OSO)"@ro .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ontologie des observatoires marins (OSO)"@fr .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ontología de los observatorios marinos (OSO)"@es .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Οντολογία θαλάσσιων παρατηρητηρίων (OSO)"@el .
