_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://github.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology> .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://service.tib.eu/webvowl/#iri=https://earthportal.eu/ontologies/OSO> .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "1.0.0 - First stable public release"@en .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "OSO" .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Această ontologie are ca scop descrierea observatoarelor subacvatice, în special a celor asociate cu Observatoarele multidisciplinare europene ale fundului mării și coloanei de apă (EMSO), care constituie un consorțiu european de infrastructură de cercetare (ERIC) din 2016."@ro .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Cette ontologie vise à décrire les observatoires sous-marins, en particulier ceux associés au réseau européen d'observatoires multidisciplinaires des fonds marins et de la colonne d'eau (EMSO), qui constitue un consortium européen d'infrastructures de recherche (ERIC) depuis 2016."@fr .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Denne ontologien har som mål å beskrive undervannsobservatorier, særlig de som er tilknyttet European Multidisciplinary Seafloor and Water Column Observatories (EMSO), som har vært et europeisk forskningsinfrastrukturkonsortium (ERIC) siden 2016."@no .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Esta ontologia visa descrever observatórios subaquáticos, em particular os associados ao Observatório Multidisciplinar Europeu do Fundo Marinho e da Coluna de Água (EMSO), que é um Consórcio Europeu de Infraestruturas de Investigação (ERIC) desde 2016."@pt .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Esta ontología tiene como objetivo describir los observatorios submarinos, en particular los asociados al Observatorio Multidisciplinar Europeo del Fondo Marino y la Columna de Agua (EMSO), que es un Consorcio Europeo de Infraestructuras de Investigación (ERIC) desde 2016."@es .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Questa ontologia ha lo scopo di descrivere gli osservatori sottomarini, in particolare quelli associati agli Osservatori multidisciplinari europei dei fondali marini e della colonna d'acqua (EMSO), che dal 2016 costituiscono un Consorzio europeo per le infrastrutture di ricerca (ERIC)."@it .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "This ontology aims to describe underwater observatories, in particular those associated with the European Multidisciplinary Seafloor and Water Column Observatories (EMSO), which has been a European Research Infrastructure Consortium (ERIC) since 2016."@en .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Η οντολογία αυτή έχει ως στόχο να περιγράψει τα υποβρύχια παρατηρητήρια, ιδίως εκείνα που συνδέονται με τα Ευρωπαϊκά Πολυεπιστημονικά Παρατηρητήρια Θαλάσσιου Βυθού και Υδροκολώνας (EMSO), τα οποία αποτελούν Ευρωπαϊκό Συνεταιρισμό Ερευνητικής Υποδομής (ERIC) από το 2016."@el .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Observatories of the Seas Ontology"@en .
