# 
# https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://data.bioontology.org/metadata/prefixIRI> "OSO:Site" .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A localized observatory site, attached to a regional facility, potentially hosting one or more measurement platforms."@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Et lokalisert observasjonssted tilknyttet en regional fasilitet, som potensielt huser en eller flere måleplattformer."@no .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Um local de observação localizado, associado a uma infraestrutura regional, podendo acolher uma ou mais plataformas de medição."@pt .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un site observatoire localisé, rattaché à un nœud régional, pouvant accueillir une ou plusieurs plateformes de mesure."@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un site observator localizat, asociat cu o facilitate regională, care poate găzdui una sau mai multe platforme de măsurare."@ro .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un sitio de observación localizado, vinculado a una infraestructura regional, que puede albergar una o más plataformas de medición."@es .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un sito osservatorio localizzato, collegato a una struttura regionale, che può ospitare una o più piattaforme di misura."@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ένας τοπικός τόπος παρατήρησης, συνδεδεμένος με μια περιφερειακή υποδομή, που μπορεί να φιλοξενήσει μία ή περισσότερες πλατφόρμες μέτρησης."@el .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Loc de observare"@ro .
