<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Subsite> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Sotto-sito di osservazione"@it .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Subsite> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Sous-site d'observation"@fr .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Subsite> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Sub-site de observație"@ro .
