# https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#MARMOR
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#MARMOR> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#MARMOR> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#MARMOR> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#hasCountry> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#France> .
